7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Soundraw and Voicemod share a solid foundation of core features including . Where Soundraw pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Music Generation, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Voicemod uniquely offers Text To Speech and Custom Voices and Real Time, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Soundraw holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Voicemod scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Voicemod comes in at a lower starting price of $4/mo, while Soundraw begins at $16.99/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Soundraw's free tier and Voicemod's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
