b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Soundraw is best suited for video creators needing background music, royalty free music production, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Voicemod, meanwhile, shines for gamers and streamers, fun voice effects, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2020, Soundraw describes itself as \"AI music generator for royalty-free background tracks.\" Voicemod, established in 2014, positions itself as \"Real-time AI voice changer for gaming and streaming.\" With 6 years between them, Voicemod brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Soundraw offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Voicemod** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to more features (3 vs 1), more competitive pricing, availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Soundraw is a poor choice — far from it. Soundraw excels in its own right, particularly for video creators needing background music and royalty free music production.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value real-time voice changing, go with Voicemod. If fully royalty-free matters more to you, Soundraw is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
